Cyberpunk style: A hacker's workspace bathed in neon blue and electric purple light, featuring multiple holographic screens floating in mid-air displaying cascading lines of code and color palette swatches. A gloved hand reaches toward one screen, dragging a vibrant color swatch that trails luminous particles. The environment is a gritty futuristic room with exposed circuitry on dark walls, chrome surfaces reflecting the colorful glow, and rain-streaked windows showing a dystopian cityscape beyond. Paint-like digital drips in cyan, magenta, and electric blue seem to melt off the floating interfaces, pooling into glowing puddles on the metallic desk surface. The atmosphere is rebellious and creative, suggesting digital customization and breaking free from default constraints.
